msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/bones/selecting.rst:107
msgid "You can deselect the active bone and select its immediate parent or one of its children using respectively :menuselection:`Select --> Parent`, :kbd:`[` or :menuselection:`Select --> Child`, :kbd:`]`. If you prefer to keep the active bone in the selection, use :menuselection:`Select --> Extend Parent`, :kbd:`Shift-[` or :menuselection:`Select --> Extend Child`, :kbd:`Shift-]`."
msgstr ""

